Bell Petroleum Services Inc said it willcontinue to talk with Regal International Inc &lt;RGL> about beingacquired, but maintained it will pursue alternatives as part ofits reorganization plan.    Any plan of reorganization Bell arrives at would be subjectto approval by the U.S. Bankruptcy Court in Midland, Texas,Bell said.    The agreement also terminates all current litigationbetween Regal and Bell involving previous reorganization plans,in which Regal attempted to acquire Bell, the company said. Reuter&#3;